Financial Reports for Subscriptions 
bookmark_border
On this page
Subscriptions revenue
Monthly music revenue summary
Monthly music label video revenue
Monthly music label assets revenue
Monthly music label subscriber revenue summary
Monthly music publisher revenue summary
Monthly music publisher subscription revenue summary
Monthly music publisher non-music subscription revenue summary

The YouTube Premium subscription reports contain revenue and view data related to YouTube Premium paid subscriptions. The specific data in the reports depend on the type of content. These reports are available on a monthly basis from the Reports page in YouTube Studio Content Manager.

The Summary report contains an aggregated view of subscription activity, the Asset Summary report provides activity at the asset level, while the Claim Raw Data report shows the activity per video, asset, country, or day.

Subscriptions revenue
Monthly music revenue summary

This report summarizes the monthly YouTube Premium subscription revenue for music content. Each row in the report includes monthly YouTube Premium revenue totals for the content. The report may contain multiple rows per type if there are revenue adjustments for the content related to backpay, conflict resolution, etc.

The reportType id for this report is content_owner_country_music_red_revenue_summary_a1.
